    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.27 / tmp + 0.74) - (v2 + 0.90 / v2 + 0.43)))
    v0 = 0.11
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.58 + v2 + 0.26)))
    v2 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.79 - v2 + 0.03) + 0.10))
